messageBody:
--- In junit@yahoogroups.com, "sariachp" <sariachp@y...> wrote:
> Hi,
>
> Can you send me an example of using the getInstance method. I don't
> know which class it is a method of.
>
> -Saritha

Saritha, the getInstance() method's job (in this case) is to return an
instance of a class with a private constructor. There's only one place
you can put it...
